## High-current connectors — must replace

> [!WARNING]
> The board ships with **2.54 mm headers (~3 A)** on `J1` / `J2` / `J3`, which carry **10–15 A**. Replace them with XT60 / 5.08 mm terminals, and run the 15 A fuse (`F1`) on an **inline blade-fuse holder in the harness**, not the PCB pin header — before powering the board.

