> [!NOTE]
> - **D1 (SMBJ12A TVS) is optional** — the board is functional without it; leave the SMB pad empty if you can't source one locally.
> - **XL4016 buck modules:** set output voltage with a multimeter **before** wiring — 6.0 V for the servo rail, 5.0 V for the 5 V rail.
> - **Encoders run on +3V3 only** — 5 V on an ESP32 GPIO permanently damages it.
> - 10 µF electrolytics: ≥16 V works, 25 V for margin. Keep the D5.0 mm body / 2.5 mm pitch to fit the footprint.
